Calculations:
Revenue Per Order: UnitPrice*OrderQuantity*(1-DiscountApplied) -> Total Revenue= SUM(RevenuePerOrderCells)
Cost Per Order: UnitCost*OrderQuantity -> Total Cost: SUM(CostPerOrderCells)
Profit per Order: Revenue - Cost -> Total profit: TotalRevenue-TotalCost
Profit Margin Per Order: Profit/Revenue -> Total Profit Margin: Total Profit/ Total Revenue
Revenue Lost to Discounts: SUM(UnitPriceCells*OrderQuantityCells*DiscountAppliedCells)
